ling and Cross-Layer Reliability_5Exntsh.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1110\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1108,'<p><img title=\"Picture - Physics-Based Electron-migration Modeling and Cross-Layer Reliability_b5xaMZ3.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1109\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1122,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1126,'<p><img title=\"Picture - Modelling the human body: from its external appearance to the hidden _q9NFo6L.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1131\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1130,'<p><img title=\"Picture - Modelling the human body: from its external appearance to the hidden _GjM06dv.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1132\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1144,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1148,'<p><img title=\"Picture - Coding Schemes with Rate-Limited Feedback that Improve over the Nofee_RAhDWFi.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1155\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1152,'<p><img title=\"Picture - Coding Schemes with Rate-Limited Feedback that Improve over the Nofee_4BqWFPd.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1154\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1216,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1220,'<p><img title=\"Picture - Adaptive MCMC for infinite dimensional Bayesian inferences_RtBsxaA.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1226\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1224,'<p><img title=\"Picture - Adaptive MCMC for infinite dimensional Bayesian inferences.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1225\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1238,'<p>上海科技大学校务委员会于2013年12月28日召开第一次会议，出席会议的校务委员会成员有：</p>\n\n<p>徐匡迪：第十届全国政协副主席、上海市人民政府原市长、中国工程院原院长、上海科技大学第一届校务委员会主任</p>\n\n<p>周小川：第十二届全国政协副主席、中国人民银行行长</p>\n\n<p>翁铁慧：上海市人民政府副市长、上海科技大学筹建工作小组副组长</p>\n\n<p>丁仲礼：中国科学院副院长、中国科学院教育委员会主任</p>\n\n<p>傅成玉：中国石油化工集团公司董事长、党组书记</p>\n\n<p>江绵恒：中国科学院上海分院院长、上海科技大学筹建领导小组副组长、筹建工作小组组长、执行委员会主席</p>\n\n<p>朱志远：中国科学院上海分院常务副院长、上海科技大学筹建领导小组成员</p>\n\n<p>会议由徐匡迪主任主持。</p>\n\n<p>根据已由院市双方核准的《上海科技大学章程》的规定，校务委员会是上海科技大学的行政决策和议事机构，由上海市人民政府委派代表、中国科学院委派代表、学校代表和社会知名人士组成，其主要职责包括：制订和修改学校章程；审定学校发展战略与规划；提名校长人选；根据校长的提名任免学校有关管理人员；听取并审定学校年度工作报告和财务预算、决算；对学校重大事项做出决策；决定其他需要校务委员会审议的事项等。</p>\n\n<p>会议听取了《上海科技大学章程》的说明；听取了学校办学理念和目标，教学、科研工作及人才队伍建设进展情况，校园建设进展情况，以及2014年主要工作的汇报；审议通过了《上海科技大学校务委员会议事规则》；审议通过了相关人事任命；原则同意上海科技大学2013年度财务决算及2014年度财务预算。会议还对其他重大事项进行了讨论。</p>\n\n<p>会议指出，上海科技大学在党的十八届三中全会关于深化教育领域综合改革战略的指导下，积极探索教育、科研、创新创业的深度融合，在办学体制、治理结构、办学与人才培养模式、人事制度、拨款制度等方面大胆改革创新，在建设过程中得到了上海市人民政府和中国科学院的大力支持，各项工作取得了重大进展。会议相信，在教育部、上海市、中科院的大力支持和学校全体教职员工的不懈努力下，上海科技大学将在2014年进一步改革创新、开拓进取，按既定目标推动各项工作取得新的成绩。</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201403061346428421.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1239\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1242,'<p>The first meeting of the University Board of Trustees was held on December 28th 2013. The attending members are:</p>\n\n<p><em><strong>Xu Kuangdi</strong></em>, Vice Chairman of 10th CPPCC National Committee; former Mayor of Shanghai, former President of the Chinese Academy of Engineering; Chairman of the University Council of the University <br>\n<em><strong>Zhou Xiaochuan</strong></em>, Vice Chairman of 12th CPPCC National Committee; Governor of the People\'s Bank of China.<br>\n<em><strong>Weng Tiehui</strong></em><strong>,</strong> Vice Mayor of Shanghai; Deputy Head of the Working Group of ShanghaiTech.<br>\n<em><strong>Ding Zhongli</strong></em>, Vice President of Chinese Academy of Sciences; Director of the Education Committee of CAS.<br>\n<em><strong>Fu Chengyu</strong></em><strong>,</strong> Chairman of China Petroleum &amp; Chemical Corporation.<br>\n<em><strong>Jiang Mianheng</strong></em><strong>,</strong> President of Chinese Academy of Sciences Shanghai Branch; Chairman of the Executive Committee of Shanghaitech.<br>\n<em><strong>Zhu Zhiyuan</strong></em><strong>,</strong> Executive Vice President of Chinese Academy of Sciences Shanghai Branch.</p>\n\n<p>The meeting was chaired by Xu Kuangdi.</p>\n\n<p>According to the By Laws of ShanghaiTech University approved by both CAS and Shanghai Municipality, the University Board of Trustees is the decision-making body of ShanghaiTech. It is composed of representatives from Shanghai Municipality, CAS, the university as well as expert from the industry. Its responsibilities include compiling and revising the By Laws, drafting the development strategy and plan; nominating the university President, appointing the administrative heads based on the President\'s nomination, reviewing the annual report, budget and final account, deciding the key issues of the university and etc,.</p>\n\n<p>The meeting reviewed the vision and goals of the university, the current status of teaching, research, recruitment, the campus construction and annual report 2014. The meeting approved the University Board of Trustees Rules of Procedure, key position appointment, as well as the final accounts of 2013 and budget for 2014.</p>\n\n<p>The University Board of Trustees pointed out that ShanghaiTech University has made considerable progress by reforming the university structure, management, nurturing of talents, human resource system and allocation of funding and has actively explored the deep integration of education, research and innovation. The members are confident that under the support of Ministry of Education, Shanghai Municipality, and the hard work of the all faculty and staff, ShanghaiTech will make new achievements in 2014.<img title=\"Picture - 201403061346428421_z38VaAJ.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1243\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1251,'<p>计算机视觉领域的著名学者马毅博士，于2014年3月以全职教授身份加入上海科技大学信息科学与技术学院，他将成为上海科技大学信息学院在计算机视觉研究方向上的带头人。</p>\n\n<p>马毅教授于1995获清华大学自动化学士学位和应用数学学士学位；1997年获加利福利亚大学伯克利分校电子工程与计算机科学硕士学位；2000年获加利福利亚大学伯克利分校数学硕士学位，同年获该校电子工程与计算机科学博士学位。他于2000至2006年任伊利诺伊大学厄巴拿香槟分校电子与计算机工程系助理教授；于2006至2011年任伊利诺伊大学厄巴拿香槟分校电子与计算机工程系副教授；于2009至2014年任微软研究院计算机视觉组主任及首席研究员。他曾获得1999年国际计算机视觉大会（ICCV）David Marr最佳论文奖，2004年美国自然科学基金（NSF）优秀青年学者奖CAREER Award和2005年美国海军部杰出青年学者奖Young Investigator Award；2011年获微软优秀员工金星奖Gold Star Award。他在2013年成为 IEEE Fellow。2007-2011，年他担任国际期刊《IEEE Trans. on Pattern Analysis and Machine Intelligence》的副主编，现任《IEEE Trans. on Information Theory》、《International Journal of Computer Vision》、《IMA Journal on Information and Inference》和《SIAM Journal on Imaging Sciences》的副主编。他还曾担任国际计算机视觉大会（ICCV）的领域主席、程序委员会主席和大会主席等职，并多次应邀出席国际会议并作报告。</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201405161418534052.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1252\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1255,'<p>Dr. Yi Ma, a famous scholar in computer vision, joined in the School of Information Science and Technology, ShanghaiTech University as a full-time professor who would lead the study of computer vision in March, 2014.</p>\n\n<p>Yi Ma received Bachelor’s degree in Automation and Applied Mathematics from Tsinghua University, Beijing, China, in 1995. He received a Master degree in Electrical Engineering and Computer Sciences (EECS) in 1997, a second Master degree in Mathematics in 2000, and the Ph.D. degree in EECS in 2000, all from the University of California at Berkeley. He served as associated professor from 2000 to 2006 and vice professor from 2006 to 2011 of the Department of Electrical and Computer Engineering, University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign. From 2009 to 2014, he served as research manager for the Visual Computing Group at Microsoft Research Asia, Beijing, China. His PhD research won the David Marr Best Paper Award at the International Conference on Computer Vision (ICCV) in 1999. He was the recipient of the Faculty Early Career Development (CAREER) Award from the National Science Foundation (NSF) in 2004. He was also the recipient of the Young Investigator Program (YIP) Award from the Office of Naval Research (ONR) in 2005. He received the Gold Star Award from Microsoft Corporate in 2009. He has served as an associate editor of the IEEE Transactions on Pattern Analysis and Machine Intelligence (TPAMI) from 2007 to 2011. He became a Fellow of IEEE in 2013. He has served as an associate editor of the IEEE Transactions on Pattern Analysis and Machine Intelligence (TPAMI). He currently serves as the associate editors for the IEEE Transactions on Information Theory, the International Journal of Computer Vision (IJCV), the IMA Journal on Information and Inference, and the SIAM Journal on Imaging Sciences. He also served as the Area Chair, the Program Chair and the General Chair for ICCV and was invited to present reports in many international conferences.</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201405161418534052_S31shdt.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1256\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1259,'<p><img title=\"Picture - 201408191139291671.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1260\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n\n<p>汤森路透(Thomas Reuters)于2014年6月发布了全球“高被引科学家”(Highly Cited Researchers 2014， http://highlycited.com)名单。我校信息科学和技术学院兼职（访问）教授崔曙光入选。高被引论文是根据Web of Science数据库统计，他引频次在所属领域同一年度发表的论文中排名前1%的论文。汤森路透分析了21个学科领域（横跨数学，工程，生物，农业，计算机，经济，材料，物理，化学等）2002-2012年间发表的高被引论文，将各学科领域发表高被引论文数量最多的研究人员选入全球“高被引科学家”名单。全球共有3215位研究人员入选，几乎囊括了各个领域最活跃和最有影响力的科学家。汤森路透也称此名单成员为 The world’s most influential scientific minds.</p>\n\n<p>Dr. Cui于1997年在北邮获得学士学位（系第一名），2000年在加拿大McMaster大学获得硕士学位，2005年在美国斯坦福大学获得博士学位。现在美国Texas A&amp;M大学电子与计算机工程系任副教授，并在上海科技大学任兼职（访问）教授。Dr. Cui的科研方向主要集中在：面向大数据的网络信息处理，认知无线电系统的优化和设计，无线传感器网络和物联网的能耗优化，估计与检测系统的跨层设计，基于可再生能源的通信系统优化设计。其已在国际一流期刊和会议上发表了过百篇论文，其中有八篇期刊文章自发表之日至今被引用次数在同期刊中排名前十（其中一篇引用次数排名第一，三篇引用次数排名第二)。Dr. Cui是IEEE信号处理协会2012年最佳论文奖获得者, 并曾担任多个国际期刊的编委(IEEE TSP, TWC, TVT, CL)，是IEEE通信协会无线技术委员会(WTC)的秘书长，IEEE信号处理协会SPCOM技术委员会的委员，并担任其工业／政府关系子委员会的主席。Dr. Cui在2013年当选IEEE Fellow（博士毕业后8年内当选为IEEE历史上最快之一），并在2014年被任命为IEEE Transactions on Big Data的Steering Committee委员，负责第一届主编的选定。</p>\n'),(1263,'<p>信息学院全体教职员工喜迎2014级秋季入学的新同学（含第一届本科生95名和第二届研究生87名）。同学们通过学校与学院安排的一系列迎新活动，加深了对上海科技大学的了解,坚定了对未来学习生活的信念。研究生课程已于9月9日正式开始。本科同学将在军训结束后正式开始他们期盼已久的大学生活。</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - Orientation 20148974.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1264\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1267,'<p>The faculty and staff of SIST joyfully welcome our new students coming in 2014, which include the first batch of undergraduate students and second batch of graduate students. Through substantial activities in the orientation, students got to know more about ShanghaiTech and strengthened their confidence towards future study and living here. The graduate courses have started since September 9. Undergraduate freshmen are going to set out for their long expected college education very soon after finishing their military training.</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - Orientation 20148974_c84HgXy.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1268\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1271,'<p>美国特拉华大学的虞晶怡副教授和卡内基梅陇大学的李昕副教授加盟上科大，成为信息学院的访问教授。</p>\n'),(1273,'<p>Prof. Jinyi Yu, Associate Professor at the University of Delaware, and Prof. Xin Li, Associate Professor at Carnegie Mellon University have joined the SIST as visiting professors.</p>\n'),(1275,'<p>自2014年7月以来加入信息学院的新老师有：耿艳林助理教授，袁晓军助理教授，罗喜良副教授，高盛华助理教授，师泽仁（Soeren Schwertfeger）助理教授，王浩宇助理教授，Boris Houska助理教授。此外已确定在2015年稍后上任的同事有：刘晓培助理教授，陆疌助理教授，孟子阳助理教授，王雄助理教授，张良峰助理教授，郑友怡助理教授。</p>\n'),(1277,'<p>The professors who have joined the SIST since July 2014 includes: Dr. Yanling Geng, Xiaojun Yuan, Shenghua Gao, Soeren Schwertfeger, Haoyu Wang, and Boris Houska as Assistant Professors, and Xiliang Luo as Associate Professor. In addition, 6 new colleagues include Dr. Xiaopei Liu, Dr. Jie Lu, Dr. Ziyang Meng, Dr. Xiong Wang, Dr. Liangfeng Zhang, Dr. Youyi Zheng will report on duty later in 2015.</p>\n'),(1279,'<p>2015年1月22日，信息学院在岳阳路校区举行首次务虚会议，全体教职员工出席，江绵恒校长等校领导及其他有关职能部门同事列席。在会议中，执行院长丁峙教授回顾了学院筹建至今教员招聘及发展情况，并转达了国际咨询委员会对学院未来发展的指导性建议。其后学院的学术、教学、研究生招生、学术讲座、公共关系等五个委员会对其工作进行了回顾，介绍了各自的章程，讨论了未来的工作计划。在听取了上述报告后，学院教师与校领导一起就学院各方面的发展进行了广泛的交流，并就学院的未来发展展开深入的探讨。</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201501310004245165.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1280\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201501310004506755.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1281\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201501310005041729.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1282\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1287,'<p>The School of Information Science and Technology (SIST) has held their first retreat meeting in the Puxi campus at Jan. 22, 2015. All presidents of ShanghaiTech including President Mianheng Jiang, and some colleagues in other functional offices has also attended this meeting. In the meeting, Prof. Zhi Ding, the executive dean reviewed the faculty recruitment and development since establishing and summarized the guiding comments from the international advisory board. After that, the chairs of Academic Committee, Curriculum Committee, Graduate Admission Committee, Seminar Committee, and Public Relation Committee reported their achievements in 2014, introduced their drafted by-laws, and discussed their future plan. After the reports, the faculty members of SIST make an extensive communication with the university leaders regarding different issues about the school development; they have also made a brainstorm about their future roadmap.</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201501310004245165_hgmDMnB.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1288\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201501310004506755_syJmdXe.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1289\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201501310005041729_ZwroWNi.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1290\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1295,'<p>在加州大学伯克利分校与上海科技大学交换计划的支持下，我校信息学院向伯克利派遣了第一批师生代表。周平强助理教授、高盛华助理教授、廖凯（二年级硕士研究生），在2015年一月份到达伯克利，开始为期半年的学习、交流与研究生活。</p>\n\n<p>根据两校协议，我校交流团代表将旁听伯克利的相关课程，并将伯克利出色的课程经验移植到上科大。年轻的教授可以通过该计划与伯克利的相关老师建立长期的科研关系。</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201502031733531115.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1296\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1299,'<p>Supported by the Berkeley-ShanghaiTech-Exchange (BeSTEC) Program, the first delegation of SIST@ShanghaiTech, consisting of Professor Pingqiang Zhou, Professor Shenghua Gao, and Mr. Kai Liao (2nd year graduate student), has started their Berkeley time from the last week of Jan. 2015.</p>\n\n<p>According to the program, professors and students of SIST can attend part of the Berkeley courses, which would later be offered to SIST students. This program will also help the junior faculty members at ShanghaiTech to build research connections with the faculty at Berkeley.</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201502031733531115_7F2rgXp.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1300\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1303,'<p>信息学院研究生刘晓晨的论文被DAC (Design Automation Conference) 2015接收。他的论文题目是“A Statistical Methodology for Noise Sensor Placement and Full-Chip Voltage Map Generation”。刘晓晨的导师是周平强教授。</p>\n\n<p>DAC是电路设计和自动化领域的顶级国际会议，每年举办一次。 今年的DAC会议将于6月份在美国旧金山召开。</p>\n'),(1305,'<p>SIST student Xiaochen Liu’s paper was accepted by Design Automation Conference (DAC) 2015. His paper is titled “A Statistical Methodology for Noise Sensor Placement and Full-Chip Voltage Map Generation”. Xiaochen’s advisor is Prof. Pingqiang Zhou.</p>\n\n<p>DAC is the premier conference for the design and automation of electronic systems. DAC 2015 will be held in San Francisco in June 2015. </p>\n'),(1307,'<p>2015年4月20日下午，信息学院学术报告讲座在我校岳阳路校区举行，斯坦福大学计算机科学系教授Leonidas Guibas带来了主题为“Networks of Shapes and Images”的报告。</p>\n\n<p>首先，信息学院执行院长马毅教授为大家介绍了Leonidas Guibas教授的学术生涯。Guibas教授是图形学方面的专家，也是美国计算机协会会士（ACM Fellow）、美国电子电气工程师协会会士（IEEE Fellow）, 获得过ACM Allen Newell奖。他的学术成果丰富，其中享誉世界的成果包括：双重散列法分析、红黑树、四边数据结构、Voronoi-Delaunay算法、EMD距离、Kinetic数据结构（KDS）、Metropolis light transport、heat-kernel signatures以及functional maps。</p>\n\n<p>Guibas教授在报告开头讲到，在科学、工程、医学和商业中，我们会面临来自各个方面的海量数据，而这些数据往往会包含几何或者视觉特征。更重要的是，我们收集到的这些几何数据集通常情况下是高度相关的。他介绍了基本的数学和计算工具，可以用来对这些相关的关系网进行建模、分析和研究。通过研究发现这些数据提供了丰富的特性。报告中，Guibas教授用了大量有趣的图片引发了师生们的强烈兴趣，报告结束后进行了广泛的交流讨论。</p>\n\n<p>【Leonidas Guibas 简介】</p>\n\n<p>       Leonidas Guibas 1976年从斯坦福大学获得博士学位，师从Donald Knuth。他之后在施乐帕克研究中心（Xerox PARC）、麻省理工学院和DEC系统研究中心（DEC SRC）工作过。从1984年开始在斯坦福大学计算机科学系任教授。他培养的博士生中，有几位已经享誉计算几何学界，例如John Hershberger、Jack Snoeyink和Jorge Stolfi，或者在计算机图形学中很有名, 例如 David Salesin、Eric Veach以及 Niloy Mitra。</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201504232315256998.JPG\" id=\"plugin_obj_1308\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1311,'<p>On April 20, 2015, Leonidas Guibas, professor of computer science at Stanford University, gave a talk named “Networks of Shapes and Images” to ShanghaiTech faculty and students.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p>Prof. Yi Ma, executive dean of School of Information Science and Technology (SIST), introduced the speaker’s academic career. As an ACM Fellow, an IEEE Fellow and winner of the ACM Allen Newell Award, Prof. Guibas is a well-known master in computer graphics. Some of his well-known accomplishments include the analysis of double hashing, red-black trees, the quad-edge data structure, Voronoi-Delaunay algorithms, the Earth Mover’s distance, Kinetic Data Structures (KDS), Metropolis light transport, heat-kernel signatures and functional maps.</p>\n\n<p>Prof. Guibas pointed out that, across science, engineering, medicine and business we faced a deluge of data coming from sensors, simulations or activities of individuals on the internet, and the data often contain geometric and/or visual characters. Furthermore, the geometric data sets we collected were frequently highly correlated, reflecting information about the same or similar entities, or echoing semantically important repetitions/symmetries or hierarchical structures common to both man-made and natural objects. He described general mathematical and computational tools for the construction, analysis and exploitation of such relational networks. By creating societies of data sets and their associations in a globally consistent way, we enabled a certain joint understanding of the data that provided the powers of abstraction, analogy, compression, error correction and summarization. Faculty and students were greatly attracted to the intriguing images Prof. Guibas showed during the talk, and had extensive discussion with him afterwards.</p>\n\n<p>Bio:</p>\n\n<p>Leonidas Guibas obtained his Ph.D. from Stanford in 1976, under the supervision of Donald Knuth. His subsequent employers include Xerox PARC, MIT, and DEC/SRC. He has been at Stanford since 1984 as Professor of Computer Science. He has produced several Ph.D. students who are well-known in computational geometry, such as John Hershberger, Jack Snoeyink and Jorge Stolfi, or in computer graphics, such as David Salesin, Eric Veach and Niloy Mitra.</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201504232315256998_OMLDqoo.JPG\" id=\"plugin_obj_1312\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1315,'<p>信息学院2015年秋季学期为研究生开设了《可再生能源系统》课程。为配合该课程教学，在教务处支持下，学院组织相关的老师和同学们前往上海电气风能有限公司/西门子风力发电设备(上海)有限公司进行实地参观学习。在该公司张毅工程师的引领下，一行人聆听了风力发电的发展现状以及该公司的发展历程，参观了2.5MW / 4MW风力发电机装配车间，并且驱车到该公司在东海旁的试验风电场感受真实的风力发电。通过参观风电企业，同学们加深了对可再生能源系统以及上海本地风电产业的认识。</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201505200733119750.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1317\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1320,'<p><i>Renewable Energy System</i> is a new graduate course offered in the fall semester of 2015. As a supplement to this course, the school has organized a field trip to a local sino-foreign wind power company, Shanghai Electric Wind Energy Co. Ltd / Siemens Wind Power Turbines (Shanghai) Co., Ltd. Thanks to the guidance of Yi Zhang, an engineer of the company, the visitors have listened to the state of the art of wind power industry in China, as well as the history of the company. After the introduction, they were guided to visit the assembly workshop of 2.5 MW / 4 MW wind turbines. Finally, they have a close look at the testing wind farm on the shore of East China Sea. The field trip has offered the students an immediate and memorable impression on renewable energy system and local wind power industry.</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201505200733119750_1PUK7EL.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1321\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1324,'<p>5月26日上午，上海博物馆副馆长胡江和校长江绵恒来到信息学院参观3D系统展示。信息学院执行院长、教授马毅陪同参观展示。</p>\n\n<p>在3D系统展示的过程中，教授虞晶怡详细介绍了3D系统的采集、传输、显示各个部分的详细情况，其中摄像头阵列能够实时采集显示3D场景令人印象深刻。随后双方探讨了在博物馆应用3D系统的可能性。江绵恒指出，实现科技与产业的结合是上科大的核心办学理念之一，希望学院与上博积极探讨，把握住这次很好的产学研合作机会。</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 20150609133045145.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1325\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201506091331003762.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1326\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201506091331137173.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1327\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1328,'<p>On May 26th, Deputy director of Shanghai Museum Dr. Hu Jiang and President Jiang Mianheng, accompanied by Professor Ma Yi, executive dean of SIST, visited the 3D Imaging Lab housed at SIST.</p>\n\n<p>Prof. Yu Jingyi demonstrated a novel 3D imaging system to the visitors and gave an in-depth presentation on its acquisition, data transmission and display modules. Of particular interest is the portable camera array that enables naked-eye 3D viewing. All visitors were impressed by the demonstration. After that, the two parties have further discussed potential collaborations on applying the 3D imaging system for a broad range of applications at Shanghai Museum. President Jiang Mianheng pointed out that, integrating research and real-life application is central to the mission of ShanghaiTech and SIST. He hopes that discussions today will lead to concrete collaboration between ShanghaiTech and Shanghai Museum in the near future.</p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 20150609133045145_qMff62E.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1329\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201506091331003762_2ZwmfSB.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1330\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n\n<p><img title=\"Picture - 201506091331137173_P1lWPJ6.jpg\" id=\"plugin_obj_1331\" src=\"/static/cms/img/icons/plugins/image.png\" alt=\"Picture\"></p>\n'),(1387,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1389,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1396,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1405,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1409,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1421,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1442,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1444,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1445,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1447,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1448,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1449,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1450,'<p><strong>Name: </strong>Cher Wang<br>\n<strong>Title: </strong>Dean<br>\n<strong>Tel: </strong><br>\n<strong>Email: </strong><br>\n<strong>Office: </strong><br>\n<strong>Homepage: </strong></p>\n'),(1452,'<p>Cher Wang has established a number of successful IT-related businesses, including founding VIA Technologies, Inc. and co-founding HTC Corporation. She is currently Chairwoman of both companies, and holds leadership roles in numerous other enterprises and organizations.</p>\n\n<p>Cher is active in the international business community, participating as an Industry Partner at the World Economic Forum and as a member of the APEC Business Advisory Council (ABAC). In 2010, Cher co-founded the ABAC Women’s Forum to identify capacity-building policy recommendations that enhance opportunities for women in business, and to hold outreach activities within APEC economies. Cher’s business achievements have been widely acclaimed in major international media.</p>\n\n<p>In addition to her business roles, Cher has always been devoted to giving back to the society with a keen focus on education. She fully embraces ShanghaiTech’s vision of emphasizing the integration of education, research and innovation, in order to further nurture outstanding talents engaged in scientific discovery, break-through inventions, and entrepreneurships.</p>\n\n<p>Cher graduated from the University of California, Berkeley, and is a devout Christian. She is married with two children.</p>\n'),(1465,'<p><strong>Title: </strong>院长<br>\n<strong>Tel: </strong><br>\n<strong>Email: </strong><br>\n<strong>Office: </strong><br>\n<strong>Homepage: </strong></p>\n'),(1466,'<p>　　王雪红院长目前也同时担任威盛电子股份有限公司（VIA Technologies, Inc.）与宏达电（HTC）等数家台湾上市柜公司董事长，并身兼香港TVB非执行董事、台湾塑胶工业股份有限公司董事与多家企业董事的职务。凭借着在科技趋势的把握和行业前瞻的卓越洞察，王院长已陆续创立了数家具有全球影响力和国际品牌的，极为成功的高科技及通讯相关企业。同时，王院长自2009年至今，一直担任「APEC企业咨询委员会（ABAC）」台湾代表。</p>\n\n<p>　　王院长于美国加州所创立的威盛电子股份有限公司，不仅成为个人计算机芯片行业的领导企业，更开发出完整的低耗能个人计算机处理器平台，带动了个人计算机丶超移动计算设备丶精简型计算机等产业与嵌入式市场的全面创新。</p>\n\n<p>　　王院长亦与友人共同创立了宏达电子（HTC），致力将计算机与通讯整合成为移动装置。在这样的愿景引导下，HTC已发展成为全球智能型手机之领导品牌。</p>\n\n<p>　　在企业经营之馀，王院长始终坚持回报社会，并特别关注教育领域。王院长非常认同为国家培养从事科学发现、高技术创新与新兴产业创业的拔尖人才的理念，并深信，好的技术教育是国家最佳的创新动力源泉。王院长利用其在高科技、通讯及移动通讯领域的卓越影响力，与教授团队同心协力，努力使得上海科技大学信息科学与技术学院在不久的将来成为国家重要的科技人才摇篮。</p>\n\n<p>　　王院长毕业于加州大学伯克利分校，事业上的成就备受各界肯定。她在2005 年曾获 《美国商业周刊》（Business Week）评选为2005 年度「亚洲之星」（Stars of Asia），「25 位改革前线领导人」（25 Leaders on the Forefront of Change）当中的「创新企业家」（Innovator），并获选为「亚洲商界十大杰出经理人」。</p>\n'),(1492,'<p>　　王雪红院长是信息科学与技术学院的首任院长，同时担任威盛电子股份有限公司（VIA Technologies, Inc.）与宏达电（HTC）等数家台湾上市公司董事长。她亦在多家企业与组织担任领导职务，事业上的成就备受各界肯定。王院长毕业于加州大学伯克利分校。</p>\n'),(1510,'<p>Cher Wang is the founding dean of the School of Information Science and Technology, as well as Chairwoman of VIA Technologies, Inc. and HTC Corporation.  She also holds leadership roles in numerous other enterprises and organizations.  Cher graduated from the University of California, Berkeley.</p>\n'),(1525,'<p>Enter your Content</p>'),(1527,'\n                    <p><strong>Title: </strong>Title here<br></p>\n                    <p><strong>PHD: </strong>PHD here<br></p>\n                    <p><strong>Tel: </strong>Tel here<br></p>\n                    <p><strong>Email: </strong>Email here<br></p>\n                    <p><strong>Office: </strong>Office here<br></p>\n                    <p><strong>Homepage: </strong>Homepage here<br></p>\n                    '),(1528,'<p>Enter your bref introduction. This content will show on list page.</p>'),(1529,'<div class=\"peppdo2\">\n<p><strong style=\"color: #AD2005;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">M</span>ain <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">R</span>esponsibility</strong></p>\n\n<p>1.学院行政事务年度规划、组织、协调和管理<br>\n2.学院年度工作计划、过程控制和考核总结<br>\n3.学院各委员会的会议组织流程、协调和保障<br>\n4.主管学院人事招聘工作和学院行政管理<br>\n5.负责院长公务活动安排、学院公务接待和综合事务<br>\n6.负责学院与各职能部门工作的沟通、协调<br>\n7.协调学院其它工作。</p>\n\n<p><strong style=\"color: #AD2005;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">M</span>inor <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">R</span>esponsibility</strong></p>\n\n<p>1.实验室建设与资产管理<br>\n2.研究生和本科生管理工作<br>\n3.科研项目管理与院长差旅<br>\n4.招生工作<br>\n5.对接部门：校办、人事、财务、科技、教务、公共服务等</p>\n\n<p><strong style=\"color: #AD2005;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">R</span>emark <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">(S</span>upporter<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">)</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>全体团队</p>\n</div>\n'),(1531,'<p><strong>Tel:  </strong>54201291<br>\n<strong>Email: </strong>zhouyu@@shanghaitech.edu.cn<br>\n<strong>Office: </strong>8号楼201室</p>\n'),(1532,'<p><span align=\"left\"><strong>Tel:  </strong>54201291<br>\n<strong>Email: </strong>zhouyu@@shanghaitech.edu.cn<br>\n<strong>Office: </strong>8号楼201室<br>\n<br>\n<strong>Main Responsibility:</strong><br>\n1.学院行政事务年度规划、组织、协调和管理<br>\n2.学院年度工作计划、过程控制和考核总结<br>\n3.学院各委员会的会议组织流程、协调和保障<br>\n4.主管学院人事招聘工作和学院行政管理<br>\n5.负责院长公务活动安排、学院公务接待和综合事务<br>\n6.负责学院与各职能部门工作的沟通、协调<br>\n7.协调学院其它工作。</span></p>\n'),(1576,'<p>The School of Information Science and Technology (SIST) at ShanghaiTech University will lead the charge in China\'s higher education reform by becoming a top academic research institution that is home to world-class research laboratories and faculty members. The School\'s Mission is to create a unique open and free academic environment that enables all researchers young and senior to achieve their full academic potentials.  The School will serve as the cradle that trains future scientists,  engineers, entrepreneurs, and industrial leaders in information sciences and technologies to play key roles in the ongoing economic transformation of China and the world.</p>\n'),(1577,'<p>Dean Cher Wang / 王雪红 院长</p>\n'),(1578,'<p>Dean Cher Wang / 王雪红 院长</p>\n'),(1581,'<p><strong>Ph.D: </strong>Bielefeld University</p>\n\n<p><strong>Tel: </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Email: </strong>ningcai@@shanghaitech.edu.cn</p>\n\n<p><strong>Office: </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Homepage: </strong></p>\n'),(1582,'<p><strong>博士: </strong>比勒菲尔德大学</p>\n\n<p><strong>电话: </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Email: </strong>ningcai@@shanghaitech.edu.cn</p>\n\n<p><strong>办公室: </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>个人主页: </strong></p>\n'),(1583,'<p><strong>RESEARCH INTERESTS</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n \n <li>\n \n Network coding\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n Classical information theory\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n Quantum information theory<br>\n \n <br>\n \n </li>\n \n </ul>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>BIOGRAPHY</strong></p>\n\n<p></p><p>Ning Cai received the B.S. degree in mathematics from the Normal College of Beijing, Beijing, China in 1982; the M.S. degree in mathematics from the Institute of System Science, Academia Sinica, Beijing, China, in 1984; and the Dr. degree in mathematics from the University of Bielefeld, Bielefeld, Germany, in 1988. During 1989-2005 he worked in the University of Bielefeld, Germany, the National University of Singapore, Singapore and the Chinese University of Hong Kong. Form 2006 to 2016 he was a distinguished professor Xidian University, China. He joined ShanghaiTech university in 2016. As a visiting professor, he visited the Technical University Of Munich, the Chinese University of Hong Kong, the University of Bielefeld , the University of South Australia, the Norwegian University of Science and Technology, and the University of Waterloo. Dr. Cai served as a IEEE IT Society Awards Committee member in 2008 and 2009, and a guest editor of joint Special Issue of IEEE Trans. on InformationTheory and IEEE/ACM Trans. on Networking, on “Networking and Information Theory”, 2006. He has served on the committees of a number of information theorysymposiums and workshops. Dr. Cai is a recipient of the 2005 IEEE Information Theory Society Paper Award for the paper “Linear network coding” and of the 2016 IEEE Eric. E. Sumner Award for “pioneering contributions to the field of network coding”, both with S-Y. R. Li and R. W. Yeung. He is a IEEE fellow. His research interests include network coding and classical and quantum information theory.</p><p></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>SELECTED PUBLICATIONS</strong></p>\n\n<p></p><p>\n \n 1. R. Ahlswede and N. Cai, Arbitrarily varying multiple-access channels: Ericson’s symmetrizability is adequate, Gubner’s Conjecture is true, IEEE Trans. on Information Theory, V. 45, No. 2, 742-749, 1999 ; Part 2. Correlated sender’s side information, correlated messages, and ambiguous transmission,  IEEE Trans. on Information Theory, V. 45, No. 2, 749-756, 1999.\n \n </p>\n \n <p>\n \n <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">2. R, Ahlswede, Ning Cai, S.-Y. R. Li and R. W. Yeung, Network information flow, IEEE Trans. on Information Theory”, V. 46, 1204-1216, 2000.</span>\n \n </p>\n \n <p>\n \n <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">3. S.-Y. R. Li and R. W. Yeung and N. Cai , Linear network coding, IEEE Trans. on Information Theory V.49, 371-381, 2003, (awarded paper).</span>\n \n </p>\n \n <p>\n \n <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">4.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"> N. Cai and R. W. Yeung, Secure Network Coding on a Wiretap Network, IEEE Trans. on Information Theory. V. 57, No. 1, pp 424-435, JANUARY 2011.</span>\n \n </p>\n \n <p>\n \n <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">5. N. Cai , Localized Error Correction in Projective Space, IEEE Trans. Inform Theory, v.59, pp. 3282-3294, 2013.</span>\n \n </p>\n \n <p>\n \n <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">6. H. Boche, N. Cai and J. N?tzel, The classical-quantum channel with random state parameters known to the sender, Journal of Physics A: Mathematical and Theoretical, (2016) 195302 (29pp) doi:10.1088/1751-8113/49/19/195302, 2016.</span>\n \n </p><p></p>\n'),(1584,'<p><strong>研究领域:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n \n <li>\n \n 网络编码理论\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n 经典信道\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n 信源编码定理\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n 量子信道编码定理<br>\n \n <br>\n \n </li>\n \n </ul>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>个人简历</strong></p>\n\n<p>      蔡宁于1982年在北京师范学院（现名首都师范大学）获得数学学士学位，1984年在中国科学院系统科学研究所获得数学硕士学位，1988年在德国比勒菲尔德大学（the University of Bielefeld）获得数学博士学位。从1989年到2005年，他在比勒菲尔德大学、新加坡国立大学和香港中文大学等高校从事研究工作。从2006年到2016年他在西安电子科技大学任特聘教授。他于2016年4月全职加入上海科技大学信息科学与技术学院任特聘教授。他2008 年和2009年曾担任IEEE信息论学会评奖委员会（IEEE IT Society Awards Committee）委员，并于2006年担任IEEE信息论学报（IEEE Trans. on Information Theory）和IEEE/ACM网络学报(IEEE/ACM Trans. on Networking)联合特刊“网络与信息论”（Special Issue“Networking and Information Theory”）的客座编辑（guest editor）. 他曾服务于多个信息论国际会议的各种组织委员会。他和李硕彦教授（S-Y. R. Li）和杨伟豪教授（R. W. Yeung）共同因论文“线性网络编码（Linear network coding）”获得2015年度IEEE信息论学会论文奖（the 2005 IEEE Information Theory Society Paper Award）；他们还因为“在网络编码领域中的先驱性贡献（pioneering contributions to the field of network coding）”一起获得2016年度的IEEE Eric. E. Sumner奖（the 2016 IEEE Eric. E. Sumner Award）。他是IEEE的fellow。 他当前的研究兴趣包括了网络编码及经典和量子信息论。</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>代表性论文</strong></p>\n\n<p></p><ul><li>\n 1. R. Ahlswede and N. Cai, Arbitrarily varying multiple-access channels: Ericson’s symmetrizability is adequate, Gubner’s Conjecture is true, IEEE Trans. on Information Theory, V. 45, No. 2, 742-749, 1999 ; Part 2. Correlated sender’s side information, correlated messages, and ambiguous transmission,  IEEE Trans. on Information Theory, V. 45, No. 2, 749-756, 1999.\n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n 2. R, Ahlswede, Ning Cai, S.-Y. R. Li and R. W. Yeung, Network information flow, IEEE Trans. on Information Theory”, V. 46, 1204-1216, 2000.\n </li>\n \n <li>\n <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">3. S.-Y. R. Li and R. W. Yeung and N. Cai , Linear network coding, IEEE Trans. on Information Theory V.49, 371-381, 2003, (awarded paper).</span>\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">4. N. Cai and R. W. Yeung, Secure Network Coding on a Wiretap Network, IEEE Trans. on Information Theory. V. 57, No. 1, pp 424-435, JANUARY 2011.</span>\n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">5. N. Cai , Localized Error Correction in Projective Space, IEEE Trans. Inform Theory, v.59, pp. 3282-3294, 2013.</span>\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">6. H. Boche, N. Cai and J. N?tzel, The classical-quantum channel with random state parameters known to the sender, Journal of Physics A: Mathematical and Theoretical, (2016) 195302 (29pp) doi:10.1088/1751-8113/49/19/195302, 2016.</span>\n \n </li></ul><p></p>\n'),(1585,'<p><strong>博士:  </strong>比勒菲尔德大学<br>\n<strong>电话: </strong><br>\n<strong>Email:  </strong>ningcai@@shanghaitech.edu.cn<br>\n<strong>办公室: </strong><br>\n<strong>研究领域:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>网络编码理论</li>\n	<li>经典信道</li>\n	<li>信源编码定理</li>\n	<li>量子信道编码定理<br>\n	 </li>\n</ul>\n'),(1586,'<p><strong>Ph.D:  </strong>Bielefeld University<br>\n<strong>Tel: </strong><br>\n<strong>Email:  </strong>ningcai@@shanghaitech.edu.cn<br>\n<strong>Office: </strong><br>\n<strong>Research Interests:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Network coding</li>\n	<li>Classical information theory</li>\n	<li>Quantum information theory<br>\n	 </li>\n</ul>\n'),(1587,'<p>Prof. Ning Cai/蔡宁 教授</p>\n'),(1588,'<p>Prof. Ning Cai/蔡宁 教授 (IEEE Fellow)</p>\n'),(1591,'<p><strong>Ph.D:  </strong>University of California, Berkeley</p>\n\n<p><strong>Tel:  </strong>(021)54205782</p>\n\n<p><strong>Email:  </strong>chenhao@@shanghaitech.edu.cn</p>\n\n<p><strong>Office:  </strong>Room 209, Building 8</p>\n\n<p><strong>Homepage: </strong></p>\n'),(1592,'<p><strong>博士:  </strong>加州大学伯克利分校</p>\n\n<p><strong>电话:  </strong>(021)54205782</p>\n\n<p><strong>Email:  </strong>chenhao@@shanghaitech.edu.cn</p>\n\n<p><strong>办公室:  </strong>8号楼209室</p>\n\n<p><strong>个人主页: </strong></p>\n'),(1593,'<p><strong>RESEARCH INTERESTS</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n \n <li>\n \n Computer Security\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n Mobile security, Web security, software security, network security\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n Mobile Computing<br>\n \n <br>\n \n </li>\n \n </ul>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>BIOGRAPHY</strong></p>\n\n<p></p><p>Dr. Hao Chen received his Ph.D.at the Computer Science Division at the University of California, Berkeley in 2004.  Since then, he has been on the faculty of the Department of Computer Science at the University of California, Davis.  He won the National Science Foundation CAREER award in 2007, and UC Davis College of Engineering Faculty Award in 2010.  His research has been featured in both print and broadcast media, such as the New York Times, the Sacramento Bee, and the Capitol Public Radio.  He co-founded and chaired the IEEE Mobile Security Technologies in 2012.</p><p></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>SELECTED PUBLICATIONS</strong></p>\n\n<p></p><ul style=\"\">\n \n <li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">\n \n <span class=\"title\"><strong>MAdFraud: Investigating Ad Fraud in Android Applications</strong>.</span><br>\n \n <span class=\"author\">Jon Crussell, Ryan Stevens, and Hao Chen.</span><br>\n \n <span class=\"booktitle\"><em>12th International Conference on Mobile Systems, Applications and Services (MobiSys)</em></span>, Bretton Woods, NH, USA, June 16-19, 2014.\n \n </li>\n \n <li style=\"pa