2,'<p><strong>博士: </strong>香港中文大学</p>\n\n<p><strong>电话: </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Email: </strong>fulq@@shanghaitech.edu.cn</p>\n\n<p><strong>办公室: </strong>8号楼217室</p>\n\n<p><strong>个人主页: </strong>http://sist.shanghaitech.edu.cn/faculty/fulq</p>\n'),(1673,'<p><strong>RESEARCH INTERESTS</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n \n <li>\n \n Distributed protocol design\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n Green wireless network\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n Network resource optimization\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n Wireless network control<br>\n \n <br>\n \n </li>\n \n </ul>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>BIOGRAPHY</strong></p>\n\n<p></p><p>\n \n Dr. Liqun Fu received the Ph.D. degree in Information Engineering from the Chinese University of Hong Kong in 2010, and the M.S. degree and the B.S degree (honors) both in Electrical Engineering from Tsinghua University and Xiamen University in 2006, and 2003, respectively. She visited Princeton University as a Visiting Scholar in 2009. From Sept. 2010 to Aug. 2015, she was a post-doctoral research fellow with the Institute of Network Coding of The Chinese University of Hong Kong first and then with the ACCESS post-doctoral researcher at the ACCESS Linnaeus Centre of KTH Royal Institute of Technology. She has joined the School of Information Science and Technology, ShanghaiTech University since Aug. 2015.\n \n </p>\n \n <p>\n \n Her main research interests are in the area of wireless communication and networking, with current focus on green wireless, distributed algorithm and protocol design, signal processing, and wireless network optimization and control. She has published over 20 peer-reviewed research papers in the leading journals and prestigious conferences in the related field.\n \n </p><p></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>SELECTED PUBLICATIONS</strong></p>\n\n<p></p><ul>\n \n <li>\n \n Liqun Fu, Ying Jun (Angela) Zhang, and Jianwei Huang, “Energy Efficient Transmissions in MIMO Cognitive Radio Networks,” IEEE Journal on Selected Areas in Communications (JSAC), vol. 31, no. 11, pp. 2420-2431, Nov. 2013.\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n Liqun Fu, Soung Chang Liew, and Jianwei Huang, “Effective Carrier Sensing in CSMA Networks under Cumulative Interference,” IEEE Transactions on Mobile Computing, vol. 12, no. 4, pp. 748-760, Apr. 2013.\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n Liqun Fu, Hongseok Kim, Jianwei Huang, Soung Chang Liew, and Mung Chiang, “Energy Conservation and Interference Mitigation: From Decoupling Property to Win-Win Strategy,” IEEE Transactions on Wireless Communications, vol. 10, no. 11, pp. 3943-3955, Nov. 2011.\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n Liqun Fu, Soung Chang Liew, and Jianwei Huang, “Fast Algorithms for Joint Power Control and Scheduling in Wireless Networks,” IEEE Transactions on Wireless Communications, vol. 9, no. 3, pp. 1186-1197, Mar. 2010.\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n Liqun Fu, Soung Chang Liew, and Jianwei Huang, “Power Controlled Scheduling with Consecutive Transmission Constraints: Complexity Analysis and Algorithm Design,” in Proc. of the 28th Annual IEEE Conference on Computer Communications (INFOCOM), Rio de Janeiro, Brazil, Apr. 2009. (Acceptance rate: 19.6%)<br>\n \n <br>\n \n </li>\n \n </ul><p></p>\n'),(1674,'<p><strong>研究领域:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n \n <li>\n \n 分布式算法与网络设计\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n 绿色通信\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n 网络资源调度及优化\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n 无线网络控制<br>\n \n <br>\n \n </li>\n \n </ul>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>个人简历</strong></p>\n\n<p>      付立群博士于2010年在香港中文大学信息工程学系获得博士学位,分别于2006年和2003年获得清华大学电子工程系硕士学位和厦门大学电子工程系学士学位（荣誉学士）。攻读博士学位期间，于2009年在普林斯顿大学访问半年。自2010年起至今，先后在香港中文大学网络编码研究所，瑞典皇家理工大学从事博士后研究工作。她目前的研究兴趣包括绿色通信，分布式算法与网络设计，信号处理，及无线网络控制等。近年以来，她在无线通信领域的国际重要期刊以及学术会议上发表学术论文二十余篇。</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>代表性论文</strong></p>\n\n<p></p><ul><li>Liqun Fu, Ying Jun (Angela) Zhang, and Jianwei Huang, “Energy Efficient Transmissions in MIMO Cognitive Radio Networks,” IEEE Journal on Selected Areas in Communications (JSAC), vol. 31, no. 11, pp. 2420-2431, Nov. 2013.</li>\n \n <li>\n \n Liqun Fu, Soung Chang Liew, and Jianwei Huang, “Effective Carrier Sensing in CSMA Networks under Cumulative Interference,” IEEE Transactions on Mobile Computing, vol. 12, no. 4, pp. 748-760, Apr. 2013.</li>\n \n <li>\n \n Liqun Fu, Hongseok Kim, Jianwei Huang, Soung Chang Liew, and Mung Chiang, “Energy Conservation and Interference Mitigation: From Decoupling Property to Win-Win Strategy,” IEEE Transactions on Wireless Communications, vol. 10, no. 11, pp. 3943-3955, Nov. 2011.</li>\n \n <li>\n \n Liqun Fu, Soung Chang Liew, and Jianwei Huang, “Fast Algorithms for Joint Power Control and Scheduling in Wireless Networks,” IEEE Transactions on Wireless Communications, vol. 9, no. 3, pp. 1186-1197, Mar. 2010.</li>\n \n <li>\n \n Liqun Fu, Soung Chang Liew, and Jianwei Huang, “Power Controlled Scheduling with Consecutive Transmission Constraints: Complexity Analysis and Algorithm Design,” in Proc. of the 28th Annual IEEE Conference on Computer Communications (INFOCOM), Rio de Janeiro, Brazil, Apr. 2009. (Acceptance rate: 19.6%)</li></ul><p></p>\n'),(1675,'<p><strong>博士:  </strong>香港中文大学<br>\n<strong>电话: </strong><br>\n<strong>Email:  </strong>fulq@@shanghaitech.edu.cn<br>\n<strong>办公室:  </strong>8号楼217室<br>\n<strong>研究领域:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>分布式算法与网络设计</li>\n	<li>绿色通信</li>\n	<li>网络资源调度及优化</li>\n	<li>无线网络控制<br>\n	 </li>\n</ul>\n'),(1676,'<p><strong>Ph.D:  </strong>The Chinese University of Hong Kong<br>\n<strong>Tel: </strong><br>\n<strong>Email:  </strong>fulq@@shanghaitech.edu.cn<br>\n<strong>Office:  </strong>Room 217, Building 8<br>\n<strong>Research Interests:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Distributed protocol design</li>\n	<li>Green wireless network</li>\n	<li>Network resource optimization</li>\n	<li>Wireless network control<br>\n	 </li>\n</ul>\n'),(1677,'<p>Prof. Liqun Fu/付立群 助理教授 (青年千人)</p>\n'),(1678,'<p>Prof. Liqun Fu/付立群 助理教授 (青年千人)</p>\n'),(1681,'<p><strong>Ph.D:  </strong>Nanyang Technological University</p>\n\n<p><strong>Tel: </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Email:  </strong>gaoshh@