n </li>\n \n </ul>\n \n <p>\n \n <br>\n \n </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>个人简历</strong></p>\n\n<p>      耿艳林博士在北京大学获得数学与应用数学学士学位（2006年）、信号与信息处理硕士学位（2009年），在香港中文大学获得信息工程博士学位（2012年），随后在香港中文大学从事博士后研究工作，并于2014年7月加入上海科技大学。</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>代表性论文</strong></p>\n\n<p></p><p>\n \n 1. Y. Geng and C. Nair, \"The capacity region of the two-receiver Gaussian vector broadcast channel with private and common messages\", IEEE Transactions on Information Theory, vol. 60, no. 4, pp. 2087-2104, 2014.\n \n </p>\n \n <p>\n \n 2. Y. Geng, A. Gohari, C. Nair and Y. Yu, \"On Martons inner bound and its optimality for classes of product broadcast channels\", IEEE Transactions on Information Theory, vol. 60, no. 1, pp. 22-41, 2014.\n \n </p>\n \n <p>\n \n 3. Y. Geng, C. Nair, S. Shamai Shitz and Z. V. Wang, \"On broadcast channels with binary inputs and symmetric outputs\", IEEE Transactions on Information Theory, vol. 59, no. 11, pp. 6980-6989, 2013.\n \n </p>\n \n <p>\n \n 4. Y. Geng, V. Jog, C. Nair and Z. V. Wang, \"An information inequality and evaluation of Martons inner bound for binary input broadcast channels\", IEEE Transactions on Information Theory, vol. 59, no. 7, pp. 4095-4105, 2013.\n \n </p>\n \n <p>\n \n <br>\n \n </p><p></p>\n'),(1695,'<p><strong>头衔: </strong><br>\n<strong>电话: </strong>(021) 54205157<br>\n<strong>Email: </strong>gengyl@@shanghaitech.edu.cn<br>\n<strong>办公室: </strong>8号楼105室<br>\n<strong>研究领域:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n \n <li>\n \n 多用户信息论\n \n </li>\n \n <li>\n \n 非凸优化\n \n </li>\n \n </ul>\n \n <p>\n \n <br>\n \n </p>\n'),(1696,'<p><strong>Ph.D:  </strong>The Chinese University of Hong Kong<br>\n<strong>Tel:  </strong>(021) 54205157<br>\n<strong>Email:  </strong>gengyl@@shanghaitech.edu.cn<br>\n<strong>Office:  </strong>Room 105, Building 8<br>\n<strong>Research Interests:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>network information theory</li>\n	<li>non-convex optimization</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p> </p>\n'),(1697,'<p>Prof. Yanlin Geng/耿艳林 助理教授</p>\n'),(1698,'<p>Prof. 