layer Design,” Chapter 4 in Cooperation in Wireless Communications: Principles and Applications, The Netherlands, Springer, 2006, pp. 101-126.[5] J. Xiao, S. Cui, Z. -Q. Luo, and A. J. Goldsmith, “Power Scheduling of Universal Decentralized Estimation in Sensor Networks,” IEEE Transactions on Signal Processing (TSP), Vol. 54, No. 2, pp. 413-422, February, 2006. <br>\n \n 5.  J. Xiao, S. Cui, Z. -Q. Luo, and A. J. Goldsmith, “Power Scheduling of Universal Decentralized Estimation in Sensor Networks,” IEEE Transactions on Signal Processing (TSP), Vol. 54, No. 2, pp. 413-422, February, 2006.</p>\n'),(6365,'<p>Prof. Robert Cui/崔曙光 教授</p>\n'),(6367,'<p><strong>头衔: </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>博士: </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>电话: </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Email: </strong>zczhu@@hotmail.com</p>\n\n<p><strong>办公室: </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>个人主页: </strong></p>\n'),(6368,'<p><strong>头衔: </strong><br>\n<strong>电话: </strong><br>\n<strong>Email: </strong>zczhu@@hotmail.com<br>\n<strong>办公室: </strong><br>\n<strong>研究领域:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n \n <li>\n \n <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">卫星总体设计</span>\n \n </li>\n \n </ul>\n \n <p>\n \n <br>\n \n </p>\n \n <p>\n \n <br>\n \n </p>\n'),(6369,'<p><strong>研究领域:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n \n <li>\n \n <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">卫星总体设计</span>\n \n </li>\n \n </ul>\n \n <p>\n \n <br>\n \n </p>\n \n <p>\n \n <br>\n \n </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>个人简历</strong></p>\n\n<p></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>代表性论文</strong></p>\n\n<p>1. BX-1:The Companion Microsatellite in ShenZhou VII Mission, Proceedings of the 23rd Annual AIAA/USU Conference on Small Satellite, Logan, Utah, USA，August 10-15，2009 /SSC09-IV-4.<br>\n \n 2. SZ-7伴星姿态控制系统设计及在轨试验，宇航学报，第32卷（3）（2011），495--501。<br>\n \n 3. 对空间目标成像的伴随小卫星系统设计，宇航学报，第31卷（2）（2010），329—334。<br>\n \n 4. 神舟七号微小卫星伴随飞行技术试验，空间科学学报，第29卷（3）（2009），319—325。<br></p>\n'),(6370,'<p>Prof. Zhengcai Zhu/朱振才 特聘教授</p>\n'),(6372,'<p><strong>头衔: </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>博士: </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>电话: </strong></